data.description:
.. Step into the welcoming embrace of this expansive split-level residence nestled in the heart of Empire Point! This remarkable home features four generously sized bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, offering a comfortable and spacious living experience. ROOF AND A/C from 2019!! The thoughtfully designed split floorplan ensures privacy, with the master bedroom occupying its own wing for an added touch of seclusion.

Inside, discover two distinct living areas, an inviting office space, and an abundance of natural light. The charm of this residence extends beyond its interior, with a brick exterior, complemented by the timeless elegance of hardwood flooring. An inviting front porch adds to the overall appeal, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere.

This home is not just a residence; it's a canvas of potential. Whether you envision it as your primary home or recognize its unique floor plan and prime location as an excellent investment opportunity for a PadSplit/short-term rental, the possibilities are endless. Don't miss the chance to make this distinctive property your own! Home is in excellent condition but could also be a great candidate for a renovation loan!
